I"ú<p>vegan, gluten-free, sugar-free</p>

<p><strong>If you love vegan milks, why not make your own?</strong></p>

<p>Type: Drink<br />
Tools: Blender, Sieve or filtering sock, funnel<br /></p>

<p><strong>Ingredients:</strong>
1c of oats, water, pinch of salt (optionally)</p>

<h2 id="prep">Prep</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Soak oats in 2 cups of water for 10m.</li>
  <li>Add 3 more cups of water and blend well.</li>
  <li>Filter through sieve or filtering sock.</li>
</ol>

<p>Keep in a fridge for up to 5 days.</p>
